Items.mt: The younger sister of the twin sisters, she does not know much about the dangers of the world and the ways of the world, and believes that human nature is good. She has the same beautiful appearance as Yoru Mei, but because of her special physique and lack of blood, she looks pale and bright, and has a more delicate aura than her sister, as if she is not in the human world.
